snippet.title: Haunted: Attack of the Dead Men - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Haunted: Attack of the Dead Men is coming on 6th August 2024, 109 years after the titular battle that took place at Osowiec Fortress.

Download the demo here: 
- Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2157920/Haunted_Attack_of_the_Dead_Men/
- itch.io: https://gamebeastproductions.itch.io/haunted-attack-of-the-dead-men
